# The repository-root .gitignore ignores every "screenshots/" directory, but this project commits
# its reference images as the regression baseline. Re-include those directories here so the
# *-reference.png files can be tracked; the per-run *-current.png / *-diff.png stay ignored below.
!collections/**/screenshots/

# generated screenshots that we don't want to commit
*-current.png
*-diff.png

# Bloom-regenerated book files. When the tests run, Bloom rewrites/copies these into each book
# folder every run, so they are outputs, not fixtures. They are NOT the change-detection baseline
# (that is the committed *-reference.png), so we do not track them. Genuine fixture inputs stay
# tracked: *.htm, meta.json, appearance.json, image*.png, customCollectionStyles.css,
# ArithmeticTemplate.css, publish-settings.json.
collections/**/branding.css
collections/**/appearance.css
collections/**/defaultLangStyles.css
# origami.css is a shipping support file: BringBookUpToDate copies the current
# output/browser/bookEdit/css/origami.css into every book folder (see BookStorage
# supportFilesToUpdate / CssFilesThatAreAlwaysWanted), so it is an output like the three above,
# not a fixture. Keeping it tracked made it drift every run; leaving it untracked also lets these
# tests catch any unexpected change in what Bloom copies from the distribution.
collections/**/origami.css
collections/**/langVisibility.css
collections/**/thumbnail.png
collections/**/coverImage*.jpg
collections/**/license.png
collections/**/made-with-bloom-badge*.svg
collections/**/lang-qr-code.png
collections/**/history.db
# Branding xmatter stylesheets copied in for whichever branding/xmatter is active (e.g. a
# branding that uses a custom xmatter like Uzbekistan2023-XMatter.css). Normally the final
# switch back to Default removes these, but a test run interrupted mid-branding can leave them.
collections/**/*-XMatter.css
# Branding logos copied into the book folder for whichever branding is active. A new branding
# tested here may introduce more logo files that should be added below.
collections/**/USAID_*
collections/**/Uzbekistan-*
collections/**/UEEP\[*\]*.svg
collections/**/BloomLocal.svg
collections/**/BloomWithTaglineAgainstLight.svg
collections/**/Bloom Against Light HD.png

# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
